        <Parent_String>handmade brick [300257776], brick by technique: shaping process [300010640], brick by technique [300157781], brick (clay material) [300010463], clay by product [300010462], clay [300010439], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
